# CLAUDE.local.md (example — copy to CLAUDE.local.md, then edit)

Per-developer overrides that should not be committed. This file is ignored via `.gitignore`. Use it for:

- Personal Twitch developer credentials used during testing.
- Alternate filesystem paths for the library root on your machine.
- Opt-in verbose logging toggles.
- Notes to yourself about open experiments on this checkout.

## Example

```
## Environment
- Library root on this machine: /Volumes/SomeDrive/sightline-lib
- Twitch dev app: "sightline-dev-<yourname>"

## Preferences
- Prefer `pnpm tauri dev --no-watch` while hacking Rust
- Default log level: debug
```
